13:15.545 --> 13:17.339
Didn't you?

13:17.380 --> 13:18.924
(QUIETLY): Yes.

13:18.965 --> 13:20.884
(LOUDER): Yes.

13:20.926 --> 13:23.595
- Your Honor, Ms. Soulless-Papagian...
- Solis-Papagian...

13:23.637 --> 13:25.180
- Solis-Papagian...
- Solis-Papagian...

13:25.222 --> 13:27.140
- Did you take it outside?
